statlib
-------

go library for commonly used statistical computations, optimized for performance 

Test
----

Run the following to execute the test suite
    
    go test ./... 


Usage
-----

Computing the value of 12!:

    package main

    import (
       "fmt"
       "github.com/xnacly/statlib"
    )

    func main() {
        fmt.Printf("12! = %d\n", statlib.Fac(12))
    }


Choosing 3 possibilities out of 6 options:

    package main

    import (
       "fmt"
       "github.com/xnacly/statlib"
    )

    func main() {
        fmt.Printf("6nCr3 = %d\n", statlib.BinomialCoefficient(6, 3))
    }
